# Versionamento
.git
.gitignore
.github

# node_modules e artefatos de build em qualquer lugar
**/node_modules
**/.turbo
**/.next
**/.expo
**/dist
**/build

# Logs e temp
*.log
.DS_Store
**/.cache
**/coverage

# .env (segredos vêm via env do Lightsail)
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Admin e mobile: só os manifests bastam (workspace resolution)
apps/admin/**
!apps/admin/package.json
apps/mobile/**
!apps/mobile/package.json

# IDE e docs
.vscode
.idea
SESSION-*.md
docs/
*.md
!README.md
